column4: ubottu is just a bot, if he/she/it said something to you it was probably from someone in the channel
sure there wasn't a 'f' in that somewhere?

I weren't here.. I just logged on.. but this channel (and it's participants) are pretty picky about the language.. bad words, even in abbreviations aren't allowed.. omfg would be considered bad.. omg shouldn't be a problem if you ask me
